Parameters
backupManagementType
Nullable<BackupManagementType> Nullable(Of BackupManagementType)

Type of backup managemenent for the backed up item. Possible values include: 'Invalid', 'AzureIaasVM', 'MAB', 'DPM', 'AzureBackupServer', 'AzureSql'

workloadType
Nullable<DataSourceType> Nullable(Of DataSourceType)

Type of workload this item represents. Possible values include: 'Invalid', 'VM', 'FileFolder', 'AzureSqlDb', 'SQLDB', 'Exchange', 'Sharepoint', 'DPMUnknown'

sourceResourceId
String String

ARM ID of the resource to be backed up.

policyId
String String

ID of the backup policy with which this item is backed up.

lastRecoveryPoint
Nullable<DateTime> Nullable(Of DateTime)

Timestamp when the last (latest) backup copy was created for this backup item.

friendlyName
String String

Friendly name of the VM represented by this backup item.

virtualMachineId
String String

Fully qualified ARM ID of the virtual machine represented by this item.

protectionStatus
String String

Backup status of this backup item.

protectionState
Nullable<ProtectionState> Nullable(Of ProtectionState)

Backup state of this backup item. Possible values include: 'Invalid', 'IRPending', 'Protected', 'ProtectionError', 'ProtectionStopped', 'ProtectionPaused'

lastBackupStatus
String String

Last backup operation status. Possible values: Healthy, Unhealthy.

lastBackupTime
Nullable<DateTime> Nullable(Of DateTime)

Timestamp of the last backup operation on this backup item.

extendedInfo
AzureIaaSVMProtectedItemExtendedInfo AzureIaaSVMProtectedItemExtendedInfo

Additional information for this backup item.
